text: "My Kind of Woman/My Kind of Man" is a 1999 song by country singers Vince Gill and Patty Loveless. It was taken from Gill's eighth studio album The Key and Loveless' second compilation album Classics. It went to number 27 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs charts and number 22 on the Canadian RPM Country Tracks charts. Category:1999 songs Category:Country songs Category:Vince Gill songs
